{"tid":86983,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超越宮崎駿！新海誠《你的名字》成為全球總票房最高的日本電影！","createTime":"2017-01-19T12:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T07:15:56.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"696feeb3b9f5c9ddd61b3ea084624d7acff67377","tid":86983,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61823/58800dff17716.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61823%2F58800dff17716.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1000efe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本動畫電影導演新海誠去年的最新力作《你的名字》在日本以至於各個亞洲國家都掀起了可怕的觀影熱潮，讓新海誠晉升成為國民級的大物動畫導演，《你的名字》除了在日本本土已經突破 200 億日幣票房之外，根據美國《BOX OFFICE MOJO》的統計，新海誠《你的名字》已經正式打破宮崎駿的紀錄，成為日本在全球票房上成績最高的影視第一名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61823/58800df8e9d25.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61823%2F58800df8e9d25.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c2f436b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼新海誠《你的名字》所超越的宮崎駿電影，正是 2001 年上映、被譽為「神作」的《神隱少女》，宮崎駿這部動畫電影由於在歐美廣為人知，堪稱是最出名的日本動畫電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61823/58800dfc29327.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61823%2F58800dfc29327.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f6d7a6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼根據最新統計，新海誠《你的名字》在全球已經收入了 2.81 億美元，打破了當年《神隱少女》2.749 億美元的紀錄，而造成這樣的差距，其實有一個很關鍵的原因，就是在於中國票房。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61823/58800e7199eb8.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61823%2F58800e7199eb8.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9ad852af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《神隱少女》當年並沒有像《你的名字》到中國大規模上映，因此可以見到《神隱少女》在日本本土的地位依然無法撼搖，以 308 億日圓的票房高居第一，不過老爺子在海外被新海誠給超越了，不知道是不是能夠觸動宮崎駿再度復出，為我們帶來一部更嶄新的動畫電影呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61823/58800dfa93e73.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61823%2F58800dfa93e73.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=3bb4a85d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31689a1ab6ef71e5ca3237a2693166b4406d2cb1","tid":86983,"uid":30723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"宮崎駿係九十年代係無敵，而家係無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再鋒利既刀"},{"pid":"fcd052c5a2e88ee9f34946b35411c802242417e0","tid":86983,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"好明顯宮崎駿意像高幾班"},{"pid":"d891c0a25f1ff2427ad9d85157d1cfbfacaed2e3","tid":86983,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"中國票房賣斷左 收唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ed6f94b1c75f3841e621328525abb2b968ac97","tid":86983,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"點解你的名字吹到咁大，神作秒速五厘米反而冇人識"},{"pid":"1b49ffdc0deeb656e16c9bfee03618309044e76d","tid":86983,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"Overrated."},{"pid":"197041fff872814beecc8ab95f062aa2412c5442","tid":86983,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"inflation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c26ac591012b4a5754d35cba7bf56ba1e2ddf3","tid":86983,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"未計通漲所以其實仲未超越（好似係）"},{"pid":"ec06b95e33c6e7a3a19ced591daead51b2fc47f4","tid":86983,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  新海誠有d中二，<br />\n就算5cm都好毒男tone，類似那些年果種味道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申  藍絲 睇新海誠係睇景"},{"pid":"d62286c0ef8c99b8b04dfeb600a4a91f58811a8d","tid":86983,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"overrated as fuck"},{"pid":"0f26d520b33d69e72c63ce716e8d37a54430bb81","tid":86983,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"你的名字係幾好睇既<br />\n<br />\n但超越唔到千尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb250d4bc86397d263daa57d8d24dfd845255b9","tid":86983,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"但超越唔到幽靈公主"},{"pid":"c9dc9d835098e2652dfeb2362ea793b16f2a53d0","tid":86983,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你的名字係幾好睇既<br />\n<br />\n但超越唔到千尋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真"},{"pid":"c90d70dc91bfa946a59660fc0bbf010122452ce8","tid":86983,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"多人睇過套戲同超唔超越到係兩回事<br />\n搵10個睇過兩套戲既人問佢邊套好睇d 結果一目了然<br />\n媒體成日拎新海誠同宮崎駿比 新海誠都臉紅"}]}